Supergirl - Season 3 - Episode 6
Because of Alex's difficult breakup, Kara and Alex travel together to their childhood's home to spend some quite time away from the city.
We are brought back ten years ago, when they were teenage girls.
Kara's friend got killed. Kara and Alex decided to take it upon themselves to solve this crime.
Finally they discovered that it was the sheriff trying to cover his tracks from a drug deal he made that Kara's friend witnessed.
In the present, Kara and Alex both dreamed of this adventure and it pull them closer because that was the first time ever that they teamed up.
In the end we see them driving back to the city.
